<div class='spoiler'>
This answer contains spoilers…
<span class='spoilerAnswerText'>
<a class="jsShowSpoiler spoilerAction">(view spoiler)</a><span class="spoilerContainer" style="display: none">[
  
    It was definitely Jugga. The man who cut the rope is described to be a "big" man and Iqbal was anything but big. Earlier in the book Iqbal is describe<a href="#" rel="nofollow noopener">…more</a>
    It was definitely Jugga. The man who cut the rope is described to be a "big" man and Iqbal was anything but big. Earlier in the book Iqbal is described to be "small and somewhat effeminate".<a href="#" rel="nofollow noopener">(less)</a>
  
 <a class="jsHideSpoiler spoilerAction">(hide spoiler)</a>]</span>
