<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">I feel it&apos;s more of a general comment than a question. Yes the story isn&apos;t exactly new if you consider the writings of the same genre by many other au<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">I feel it's more of a general comment than a question. Yes the story isn't exactly new if you consider the writings of the same genre by many other authors at that time, but personally speaking, Singh's storytelling is totally of a different level. I haven't read all other relevant works, if course; but you know an exceptional work when you read one.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
